" :set number
" :set tabstop=4       " Sets the tab width. Not what I want.
:set softtabstop=4     " Sets the amount by which stuff is indented by pressing TAB.
:set shiftwidth=4      " Sets the amount by which stuff is moved by reindent and autoindent.
:set expandtab         " Insert spaces instead of tab characters
:set autoindent
:set background=dark
:set scrolloff=5
:set showmatch
:set noswapfile
:syntax enable
